Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have any of your dear friends ever said\N"Please!" asking you to do something?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you see your good\Nfriend having a hard time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you can't just let it be, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was able to reach this point\Nbecause many people helped me a lot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rosetta, please don't look so sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be all right.\NDon't worry. Let me handle this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my turn to help you\Nthis time! Okay? Okay? Okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:01:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss hajimari wa \Naka to kuro no Passion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toki ni urahara na kokoro o tayori ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss kirifuda wa mirai o kaeru Mission{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi ni aimai na kotae wa iranai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arienai genjitsu minai furi shite mo Bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egatai shinjitsu\NCan U feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesshiyasui jibun ni Say What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomadou iibun {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' samenai yume ochiteku sadame{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in U hikikae ni subete ushinatte mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Another Amazing Newcomer."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it! I really hate \Nit! Please do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Now" is easy for you to say, but I cannot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it another second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, why don't you give this a try too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from China, so I bet you\Nalready know this! Cat's paws martial arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will calm your feelings, meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that phony martial art.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phony?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot just ignore what you just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that?! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If what you said is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what about that correspondence class
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I took all week?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so irresponsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to do with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this! Oh, I'm in shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Anyway, do something about this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now, now, now, now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I do {\i1}not {\i0}want to live in the \Nroom right underneath Sora's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:38.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who will be the top star someday\Nshould not live in the room underneath Sora's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So change my room right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now! Now now now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's supposed to unite\NKaleido Stage now that Miss Layla's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overdoing it doesn't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a welcoming party!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A welcoming party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! A welcoming party for the newcomers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we invite Mr. Leon and May and have fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we can be more friendly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll be fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, I'll talk to Miss Sarah later too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can she come up with holding\Na welcoming party after what May said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to be a gag character,\Nbeing someone like her could be a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to be a gag character?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I think a cake is a must!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A break-in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like the shower's running.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of robber takes a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... She's coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what is going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--but in the meantime...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, what are you doing? \NLeggo! I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, what are you doing here, Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're being chased by your agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told my agent I wanted \Nto join Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my agent is such a blockhead,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she wouldn't listen to me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to join Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. After I saw you and Miss Layla\Nperform the legendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so moved by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wished I could have that\Nkind of amazing applause too, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go back to my agent anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to do anything I can to help\Nyou since you helped me so much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my agent finds me, she will punish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What kind of punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she's not going to give\Nyou ten lashes or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right! Not just ten!\NMore like a thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thous--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand lashes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you're the only\Nperson I can depend on right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything! Cleaning or laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't hesitate to ask me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear in the fro--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were able to\Nswitch to the room over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet if I hold a welcoming\Nparty, we can get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can! We can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking at her like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she doesn't seem like a\Ndiabolo prodigy girl at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to make sure to protect her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The appearance of stars that\Nwill influence Sora's Sagittarius...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many, they almost eclipse\NSagittarius and its dreams of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the path to be a real\NKaleido Star will be a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--May, Good Morn--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Miracle elevator, shut, shut, shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. I thought... I'm kinda\Nin the mood to eat a lot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triple Food Get!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'll eat in my room today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I'm going to\Nhold a welcoming party tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, you come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She said a welcoming party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So, please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-mazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I tried to wash them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you didn't hurt yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to clean the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to replace the light bulb...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you rescue me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't paying attention, \Nand I got sucked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how did it feel when you were\Ndoing the legendary great maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During practice, I thought about it a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I got anxious sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't scared,\Nbecause I was with Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also going to try out for the trapeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you serious, Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... I don't think we can\Nmake changes like that now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you increase my stage time, the\Nquality of the performance will improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's your partner, and you're trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying you should eliminate her turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But her appearance will be\Nless than five minutes like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that she's \Nworth only that much now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't like it, she can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon's suggestion is reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange, don't leave in\Nthe middle of the performance again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make no promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't take a bath \Nwhile I'm gone. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was uncalled for!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the other ensembles \Nare also shortened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's practically a one-man show for Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Mr. Leon's instructions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how everyone feels about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Kaleido Stage needs Mr. Leon right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone, let's change the mood,\Nand do our best to make the show exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best on stage again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing I ask from all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have no knowledge of her coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hear something, please contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you think Sora's\Nperformance is a little flat lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you noticed that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sora's number one fan, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know losing Layla means a lot to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the guy who joined this\Ntime can be a good partner for Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance, can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the spirit of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can see me are\Nthe chosen ones for the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I already found those who were able\Nto perform the legendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my new purpose is to find\Nsomeone who can be a real star.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I wish I could try the swing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she can't see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we just have a \Ndaytime performance today,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we go to see the Boss\Ntogether after the performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I should go see\NSora's performance for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of practice they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are certainly impressive, May Wong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor, please let me\Nappear on the real stage soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be frank with you, my abilities\Nare better than Sora Naegino's!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should hurry up\Nand pull her from the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make me the leading star.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think everyone should be\Nhonest and admit the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for Mr. Leon that he\Nhas such an amateur as his partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage doesn't need\NSora Naegino. Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you talking about Sora like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know Sora's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know her abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her abilities are no match for mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can someone like you\Nknow anything about Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! Aren't you Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The diabolo star?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be a diabolo genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is a Kaleido Stage matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Your agent's looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a reason why you're\Nhere, you should talk to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be my partner the way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reduce your part further tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something like this is not Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if we can create\Nperformances with this man in the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon looked so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll come back here again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just entered the Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that Rosetta has imposed on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder why\NRosetta came to Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta just ran through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The agent who whips her a thousand times?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, get down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to Rosetta's story!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta wants to join Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cancel the contract with my agent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work for you for a newcomer's fees!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you say, Kalos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have your own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think we should take\NRosetta's feelings into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't make it on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kid anymore, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you listen to what I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is very special to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought that perfecting the\Nperformance was the most important thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they taught me the performance was\Nsomething we create with the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get back the feelings\NI had when I started doing diabolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I saw Sora and Miss Layla\Nperform the legendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the door which had been\Nclosed inside of me finally opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wished I could perform an\Namazing show like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I can think about every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time,\NI aspired to be like somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to appear on stage with Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even do the trapeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so reckless, Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta... she's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm most afraid of, Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you may turn into\Na diabolo machine again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be certain, I'm the one who trained\Nyou so hard when you were little,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you became the youngest\Nchampion on record in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you strove for greater perfection,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you tended to drive \Nyourself into corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's tough to see you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who raised you like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you put yourself in\Na tough environment again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, you were scary when\NI was little, and you were strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm very grateful\Nthat you taught me diabolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be a machine anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll be mortified and she'll cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll have to go through \Nall kinds of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she won't be able to smile all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think she'll\Nhave time to be a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place that let\Nyou regain your smile, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you to take care of Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when she does diabolo performances,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to pay the \Nfees we already agreed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I can stay here. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some business with\Nother artists, so I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me when you have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're such a nice mother and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.61,0:22:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May and Leon didn't show up.
